{"tid":344010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【為港爭光】譚芷昀《全美一叮》晉級 驚訝獲得Golden Buzzer","createTime":"2017-08-02T02:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T17:00:11.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5eff1f48c98a3d9c387d079f3fdade1bbcc2b7f","tid":344010,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:53:08.000Z","msg":"【有片睇】萬眾期待，9歲的「香港小巨肺」譚芷昀（Celine）今日出戰美國真人騷《全美一叮》（America's Got Talent（AGT））的最新一集，終於播出。穿上金色連身裙的Celine上台淡定，向評判表示今次不會選唱偶像Celine Dion的歌曲，這次會選唱《How Am I Supposed To Live Without You》（原唱者是Michael Bolton），開腔即令評判團搖頭驚嘆，全場觀眾歡呼，為她著迷，台下Celine的爸爸媽媽及妹妹亦興奮大叫。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n這集特別嘉賓評判Laverne Cox笑言想食了Celine及帶回家，大讚Celine聲音令人驚歎及有天份，最後更按下「Golden Buzzer」，讓Celine順利晉級。Celine聞言台上呆了，任由祝賀紙碎在身邊散落。"},{"pid":"93ae661524ecfe9b12361e50beca87f08eb2948e","tid":344010,"uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/105347_0cdc5682a8a5137662ea6263bfc6e84c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F105347_0cdc5682a8a5137662ea6263bfc6e84c.jpg&h=88c53e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勁"},{"pid":"3e72fda33d9fede0b72c54d5d90d88c8399f61a7","tid":344010,"uid":26700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9ZbP7Fkzug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT9ZbP7Fkzug&d=9BvQd%2Fl7g%2B68%2F82dVwp3Chv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b136863a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9ZbP7Fkzug</a>"},{"pid":"9200e0fdf08d51d3d622c6ae0daf926f6bf2f61d","tid":344010,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"佢老豆今鋪無出嚟攞彩？"},{"pid":"e6a2657d5ebbf837b8ea64ab5ff74d444835efb1","tid":344010,"uid":36820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T